{"title":"缓存更新策略","uid":"170ae045f381d8d39d07812ade26def7","slug":"缓存更新策略","date":"2018-05-24T04:59:36.000Z","updated":"2025-04-30T08:11:18.902Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/缓存更新策略.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"读取步骤\"><a href=\"#读取步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"读取步骤\"></a>读取步骤</h1><ol>\n<li><p>读取</p>\n<ul>\n<li>读取数据库数据</li>\n<li>成功 -&gt; 写入缓存</li>\n<li>失败 -&gt; 不写入缓存</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>更新</p>\n<ul>\n<li>更新数据库数据</li>\n<li>成功 -&gt; 将缓存标记失败, 不要写入缓存.<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>两个并发操作，一个是更新操作，另一个是查询操作，更新操作删除缓存后，查询操作没有命中缓存，先把老数据读出来后放到缓存中，然后更新操作更新了数据库。</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>插入</p>\n<ul>\n<li>插入数据库</li>\n<li>成功 -&gt; 不写入缓存.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>刷新内存，以memcached为例，新增，修改和删除操作，一般采用lazy load的策略，即新增时只写入数据库，并不会马上更新Memcached，而是等到再次读取时才会加载到Memcached中，修改和删除操作也是更新 数据库，然后将Memcached中的数据标记为失效，等待下次读取时再加载。</p>\n","text":"读取步骤 读取 读取数据库数据 成功 -> 写入缓存 失败 -> 不写入缓存 更新 更新数据库数据 成功 -> 将缓存标记失败, 不要写入缓存. 两个并发操作，...","permalink":"/post/缓存更新策略","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":349,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"缓存","slug":"缓存","count":1,"path":"api/categories/缓存.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"缓存","slug":"缓存","count":2,"path":"api/tags/缓存.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">读取步骤</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Weiba","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/24520686?v=4","link":"/","description":"啊 又忘了更新了！","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/xweiba","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Spring RMI 远程函数调用","uid":"1e49212fb32c9d3364917f80982bd0ed","slug":"Spring RMI 远程函数调用","date":"2018-06-08T04:44:05.000Z","updated":"2025-04-30T08:11:18.863Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Spring RMI 远程函数调用.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"1.需要分离出来的类- 实体类- dao层, 直接在server端实现. OSS 封装为接口 阿里云 与 七牛云阿里云方法: OSSClient getOssC...","permalink":"/post/Spring RMI 远程函数调用","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":471,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Spring","slug":"Spring","count":7,"path":"api/categories/Spring.json"}],"tags"